description:
Live & Indestructible is an EP album by American rock band Disturbed. It was released on September 30, 2008, exclusively through iTunes Store, and then on October 7, 2008, it was available on other online retailers. 

It features three live tracks, from Disturbed's first online concert at Deep Rock Drive.
